WEBVTT

00:07:29.268 --> 00:07:32.621
is quality of social relationships.

00:07:32.621 --> 00:07:35.498
Not only in humans.

00:07:35.498 --> 00:07:38.844
And look at those great-grandmothers.

00:07:38.846 --> 00:07:44.000
So now, this idea 
that if we go deep within,

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:46.570
we are irredeemably selfish,

00:07:46.570 --> 00:07:49.224
